long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Welcome to Arazim Project's TAU Factor extension!

We store previous exam grade histograms and data (average, median, standard deviation) for your comfort to download at https://arazim-project.com/courses/grades.json.

You may also use Dib It, Arazim Project's TAU Factor or TAU Search which utilize this information.

The current data was generously provided by TAU Factor (which sadly can't operate anymore) but new data is added by you, by using this extension.

Important: If you encounter any issues with this extension, please don't hesitate to reach out at our contact page or via GitHub Issues. The extension does not do anything without you clicking the buttons and choosing to do so.
